{"tid":753432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呃like不成　兩成小學生不開心","createTime":"2018-07-23T15:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T15:40:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42457407d8286ffaeb08fea35cbf0dd22a275213","tid":753432,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180723/20457539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F20457539&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a2fd0dab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F20457539&h=2f738c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180723/20457539</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月23日 <br />\n<br />\n呃like不成　兩成小學生不開心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180723/large/23la4p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180723%2Flarge%2F23la4p6.jpg&h=ba92cdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■團體促父母趁子女年幼灌輸正確上網態度。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】潮流興呃like，有醫學團體的調查發現，22%小學生和27%受訪中學生因在社交媒體「like」數較少而不開心，更有51%受訪中學生稱曾被網絡欺凌。若中學生經常上社交媒體，憂鬱、自卑等比率會較高。<br />\n<br />\n香港兒科醫學會及香港兒科基金今年5至6月進行香港首個青少年使用社交媒體狀況與精神健康關係調查，結果發現使用社交媒體帶來的問題會隨年齡增長浮現。<br />\n<br />\n受訪小學生及中學生分別有22%和27%因上載內容較少「讚好」而不開心，29%小學生和51%中學生更稱曾被網絡欺凌。本身是醫生的兒科基金秘書長王曉莉表示，中學生經常上社交媒體會引致負面情緒，感到空虛孤獨、有壓力、憂鬱、自卑等的比率亦較高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三成學生日花9小時上網<br />\n<br />\n2,045名受訪青少年中，有93%有使用社交媒體，18%稱課餘用7小時或以上使用社交媒體，更有32%日花9小時以上，另78%曾在午夜回覆訊息。王曉莉認為，青少年應平衡現實及網上生活，多參與課外活動，就不用依靠網上獲取關注。<br />\n<br />\n結果又顯示68%受訪學生因經常「在線」而感到疲累，王稱，時下年輕人出生於數碼年代，朋輩間的網絡滲透度高，青少年習慣在社交媒體上快速回覆，加上近年流行限時動態（stories），需要經常發佈更新，促使他們不能「下線」。<br />\n<br />\n調查也發現小學生使用社交媒體的頻率會受家人及朋友影響，兒科基金主席陳作耘強調父母應把握「網絡教育黃金期」，在子女年幼時灌輸正確使用社交媒體態度。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁恩浩  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n窮媽媽哭崩：唔敢諗未來<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n譚惠珠發功　撐以言入陳浩天罪　「唔係有槍先叫危害國安」"},{"pid":"83b9d7685c147869edad8eb714f554cfbb1e17b5","tid":753432,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"00後渣ga"},{"pid":"e1c975b4aa09968d8ed1eb3d5ac7f9372dc8a457","tid":753432,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"同時亦都多左 learning resources <br />\n可以自學唔同範疇既事物"},{"pid":"db37af16488cd6f5ec409c8a323d379ca21932df","tid":753432,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"唔怪得仇阿達成日fb inbox人叫人like佢d post"},{"pid":"3302af3681f674885e8ee7d1488d1813cde26ce7","tid":753432,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"3個有2個都支那樣"},{"pid":"5961de46ec3835d4bb823aa8ba975263d19de465","tid":753432,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"所以child登咪成堆死假膠博attention囉<br />\n創意 波台(-&gt;感情) 尤甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360ffbb1cfe6dbe92b9b888790021eadcfd9961f","tid":753432,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n同班女神冇like me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f2623cd7f21e466e59068a9f1a0a0cb7b20e4","tid":753432,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"父母唔識買like?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baaf2109da9f85c3e3f3f6e787ddb435736d9373","tid":753432,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3302af3681f674885e8ee7d1488d1813cde26ce7","tid":753432,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:09:32.00